{"data":[{"date":"08:46 20/08","title":"Sassuolo 1-0 Inter Milan: M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/sassuolo-10-inter-milan-man-ra-quan-tham-hoa-cua-ung-vien.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sassuolo, Mauro Icardi thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Inter b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 1 v\u00e0i ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Radja Nainggolan, Keita Balde... v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim, tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, tham v\u1ecdng l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Juventus trong su\u1ed1t 7 n\u0103m qua c\u1ee7a Inter \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Sassuolo th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 C\u0110V San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, n\u00f3 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 1 c\u00e1i t\u00e1t cho s\u1ef1 \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Spalletti.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/180820_054210_81.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sassuolo, Inter \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea5t gi\u1eef Perisic tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, trong khi t\u00e2n binh Nainggolan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Nerazzurri \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, Inter tr\u00e0n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n \u1edf trung l\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a Sassuolo. V\u00ec th\u1ebf g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Spalletti \u0111ang loay hoay t\u00ecm h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u00ec Sassuolo l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 27, Miranda bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1eb3ng tay ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 Domenico Berardi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1, \u0111\u01b0a Sassuolo v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 h\u1edf t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 cho Inter trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Inter bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tung ra nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Hi\u1ec7p 1 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n cho Sassuolo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Spalletti l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Keita Balde v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 n\u00f3ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Inter kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Inter g\u00e2y ra c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh b\u00ean ph\u00eda Sassuolo c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. C\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Consigli c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Perisic, Icardi \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Inter tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n Nerazzurri c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n tham v\u1ecdng.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5679","checkdouble":"194869"},{"date":"07:28 20/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 sau c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n \u0111em v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean 30 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real trong m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean lo ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Real, khi Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale \u0111\u00e3 thay nhau l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea7y K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u1ed5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea1c quan tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a CR7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bale3-3160-1534720660.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Real Madrid v\u1eabn \u0111ang 's\u1ed1ng kh\u1ecfe' th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Bale \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real, l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111ang d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 Gareth Bale, ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Bale \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho Real sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1edbp th\u1eddi c\u01a1 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Gatafe.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e0y, Bale c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t cho Real. Ngay ph\u00fat&nbsp;th\u1ee9 7, ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales tung c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Soria m\u1edbi c\u1ee9u cho Getafe kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua. Ph\u00fat 16, Bale \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 sau qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Marcelo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu C h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bale2-7123-1534720660.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn&nbsp;Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Getafe \u0111\u00e3 rung l\u00ean. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y \u1edf b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Gareth Bale. C\u00fa t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3i b\u0103ng ra ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm t\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Carvajal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd s\u1eb5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo, Bale \u0111ang l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN. V\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Bale ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Getafe ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau Cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh. HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Carvajal c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 20 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu v\u1edbi Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, Getafe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Real. Tr\u1ea3i qua 26 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh El Geta lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid vs Getafe\" title=\"Real Madrid vs Getafe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/15347154163333.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2008/09 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Getafe \u0111\u00e3 9 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Los Blancos v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ra v\u1ec1 trong cay \u0111\u1eafng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 Real, d\u00f9 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 4-3-3 c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt lo ng\u1ea1i khi nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111ang \u1edf b\u00ean kia s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, m\u1ea3ng mi\u1ebfng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 bi\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf ph\u00eda&nbsp; trong l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe \u0111\u1ec1u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111a d\u1ea1ng h\u00f3a c\u00e1c mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lopetegui ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Courtois ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Keylor Navas v\u1eabn \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Lopetegui g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean anh \u0111\u1ec3 tin d\u00f9ng t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Courtois ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi: &quot;S\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Courtois c\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec h\u01a1n n\u1eefa cho m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Real song l\u00fac n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh Navas.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span><br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/20/Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-2-0.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5678","checkdouble":"194863"},{"date":"08:55 20/08","title":"Ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, HLV Real ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/ra-quan-thang-loi-hlv-real-ca-ngoi-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a La Liga. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap Los Blancos c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n La Liga</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid thay cho Zinedine Zidane t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c ngay sau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 khi \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Real \u0111\u1ee5ng Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 2-2 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos. Sang hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Saul Niguez v\u00e0 Koke ghi 2 b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 chung cu\u1ed9c cho Atletico c\u1ee7a Diego Simeone.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/HLV-Julen-Lopetegui-khen-ngoi-Gareth-Bale-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean La Liga b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Getafe tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0. C\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui ng\u1ee3i ca Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Gareth Bale l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Getafe, HLV Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui co man khoi dau suon se voi Real Madrid o La Liga 2018/19\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf La Liga 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4F385BC300000578-6076597-image-a-9_1534715056208.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Julen Lopetegui khen ng\u1ee3i Gareth Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian cho s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee9 3 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi kh\u00f4ng cho h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/diem-nhan-real-madrid-20-getafe-los-blancos-van-khoe-thoi-hau-cr7-180-194863.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos v\u1eabn kh\u1ecfe th\u1eddi h\u1eadu CR7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018-372-194842.html\">Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-real-madrid-vs-getafe-20-highlights-la-liga-2018-328-194857.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5677","checkdouble":"194865"},{"date":"19:56 19/08","title":"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn Juventus tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/ronaldo-khong-khien-juventus-tro-thanh-doi-bong-manh-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1eeb Real Madrid.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng sau bao ng\u00e0y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/ronaldo-juventus-chievo-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cristiano Ronaldo ra m\u1eaft Juventus kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, n\u00f3i chung kh\u00e1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Juventus c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Chievo Verona \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Serie A 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus c\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u1ed9t Juventus c\u00f3 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cRonaldo gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Juventus, c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 g\u00ec so v\u1edbi top \u0111\u1ea7u Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Juventus v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i m\u00e0 s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho Champions League. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Serie A, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u1edbi Napoli c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Inter Milan v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\">Chievo 2-3 Juventus: Ronaldo im \u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u00e0 Serie A song Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng 2017 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n Juventus...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5676","checkdouble":"194832"},{"date":"22:36 19/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra?</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edfng ASIAD, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf trong vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Theo c\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp c\u00e1c c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng knock-out, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>1. Th\u00e1i Lan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n g\u1eb7p Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 trong nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u1ee7a 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Kyrgyzstan, Bahrain, Myanmar hay Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh x\u00e1c su\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Doi-dau-Han-Quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3&nbsp;c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3, 4 t\u1ea1i hai b\u1ea3ng E, F \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD bang E\" title=\"ASIAD b\u1ea3ng E\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng E tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean khi\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam e ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u nh\u1ea5t x\u1ea3y ra, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong khi Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, Kyrgyzstan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Kim chi xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Malaysia (ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a ho\u1eb7c thua), \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u00e0 NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 b\u1ea3ng E ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu hai s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n Kyrgyzstan th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Malaysia \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c - Kyrgyzstan<br>\r\n19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8: Malaysia - Bahrain&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Bahrain<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD bang E\" title=\"ASIAD b\u1ea3ng E\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng E tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Bahrain th\u1eafng Malaysia, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E. X\u00e9t c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eafng Kyrgyzstan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec v\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Khi \u1ea5y Bahrain s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00f2a Kyrgyzstan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Son Heung-min khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai do h\u01a1n Bahrain v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Khi \u1ea5y Bahrain v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua Kyrgyzstan. Kyrgyzstan s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 th\u1eafng/thua t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Bahrain c\u00f2n Bahrain x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 do h\u01a1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i Bahrain v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u1ebfu Bahrain th\u1eafng Malaysia, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c - Kyrgyzstan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 Malaysia, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. Iran<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang F ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng F ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/BXH-bang-F-truoc-luot-dau-cuoi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng F tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B, E \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F. \u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Iran n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 thua Myanmar c\u00f2n Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng thua Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00f3, Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F v\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m (h\u00f2a Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean) ho\u1eb7c 7 \u0111i\u1ec3m (th\u1eafng Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean). Myanmar v\u00e0 Iran c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng Iran \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 3 do k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u so v\u1edbi Myanmar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng E:</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8: Iran - Myanmar<br>\r\n16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8: Saudi Arabia - Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean</p>\r\n<h2>6. Saudi Arabia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Iran kh\u00f4ng thua Myanmar c\u00f2n Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean th\u1eafng Saudi Arabia th\u00ec Iran s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng F. Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng F, do k\u00e9m Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Khi \u0111\u00f3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Saudi Arabia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194830.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-truoc-nhat-ban.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194830.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194826.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat toan t\u00ednh v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5675","checkdouble":"194840"},{"date":"23:03 19/08","title":"HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Quyet\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/069a4393-15346826740491615805468.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u 19/8, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Hajime Moriyasu th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, 1 trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i tu\u1ed5i 23 \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn: &ldquo;C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1edd k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n. D\u00f9 sao, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Hajime l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng sai khi \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sandoqa c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh tan nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i nghi c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, NHM v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;r\u1eebng&rsquo; \u1edf k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nhat-ban-thua-nhan-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194826.html\">HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn sai l\u1ea7m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat toan t\u00ednh v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5674","checkdouble":"194841"},{"date":"23:38 19/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110T\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/069a4363-153468267404575385927.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u1ed9 VH-TT-DL th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng 200 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1. Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chi\u1ebfm lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, B\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n h\u00f3a, Th\u1ec3 thao & Du l\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i 200 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tinh th\u1ea7n to l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin x\u1ea5u khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay ASIAD v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat toan t\u00ednh v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5673","checkdouble":"194843"},{"date":"00:24 20/08","title":"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/van-quyet-len-tieng-sau-thang-loi-lich-su-cua-viet-nam-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u 19/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1edd pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U23. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/069a4393-15346826740491615805468.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00fang ta th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00f4m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. Theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Quy\u1ebft, ni\u1ec1m vui n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a 90 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 6 g\u1ed3m 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 4 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng E v\u00e0 F di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y mai (20/8).</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-10-highlights-asiad-2018-325-194824.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fat toan t\u00ednh v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5672","checkdouble":"194845"},{"date":"00:48 20/08","title":"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/bao-chi-quoc-te-noi-gi-khi-olympic-viet-nam-da-bai-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. V\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Malaysia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E h\u00f4m 17/8 v\u1eeba qua, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u2018h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n\u2019 m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 19/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1edd c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i r\u1ea5t \u2018ngoan\u2019 c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 mong manh \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/ku9ggb39kijb6lpobmym.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf h\u1ebft\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 1-0, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo. V\u00e0 gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trang ch\u1ee7 L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (AFC) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 k\u00edn k\u1ebd c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, AFC c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Tokyo Sports c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng BHL Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh, \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Moriyasu Hajime l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 kho\u00e9t s\u00e2u v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan Siam Sport l\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Trang b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 non n\u1edbt kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c hay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Indonesia l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi gi\u00fap\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn chung gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai 20/8.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-dau-han-quoc-va-nhung-kich-ban-thu-vi-cho-olympic-viet-nam-tai-vong-18-asiad-168-194840.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 n\u1eb1m trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb n\u00e0o...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-duoc-thuong-nong-sau-chien-thang-truoc-nhat-ban-168-194843.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00f3ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-bat-ngo-khen-mot-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194841.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5671","checkdouble":"194847"},{"date":"20:48 19/08","title":"Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chelsea cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb Real Madrid \u201ch\u00fat m\u00e1u\u201d v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois, nh\u01b0ng nguy c\u01a1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Eden Hazard c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u201c\u0111\u1ed5i gi\u00f3\u201d s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Chelsea, tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u1eddi gian, Hazard v\u1eabn vui v\u1ebb t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Chelsea, khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n v\u1eefng t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u h\u1ebft v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u \u1edf Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c World Cup 2018: \u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c xa h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n hai n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ra sao. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u trong n\u0103m nay.\u201d \u2013 N\u00f3i v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Hazard v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi anh trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t 2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben-172-187469.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-va-chuyen-tuong-lai-hazard-nga-ba-duong-cho-ca-doi-ben-172-187469.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard: Ng\u00e3 ba \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-real-madrid-hazard-se-rat-on-nhung-thay-the-ronaldo-khong-180-191983.html\">G\u00f3c Real Madrid: Hazard s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n, nh\u01b0ng thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo? Kh\u00f4ng!</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n cung 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a khi Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Juventus, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5670","checkdouble":"194831"},{"date":"23:11 19/08","title":"Real Madrid 2-0 Getafe: Los Blancos th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/real-madrid-vs-getafe-la-liga-2082018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Bernabeu, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Carvajal v\u00e0 Bale l\u00e0 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Real Madrid.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: REAL MADRID 2-0 GETAFE\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/20/Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-2-0.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean h\u1eadu Cristiano Ronaldo. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n giao l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng, khi h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, khi m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u1ea3 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, Real c\u1ee7a k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng tr\u00f4ng gai. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a n\u00e0y (Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018), th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi b\u1ecb k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c 4-2 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y, d\u00f9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng cho s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n giao th\u1ebf h\u1ec7, song \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Los Blancos c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m. Real phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Lopetegui v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i, t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm, r\u1ed3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn l\u1ea1i 2-1 cho t\u1edbi t\u1eadn ph\u00fat 79. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Atletico g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 trong 2 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Getafe b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Getafe b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Truc-tiep-Real-Madrid-vs-Getafe-bong-da-La-Liga-201819-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Carvajal m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Real Madrid</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i Bernabeu n\u00f3i chung, tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i HLV Julen Lopetegui n\u00f3i ri\u00eang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebf ch\u1ebf h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1eefa. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m nh\u1ecf b\u00e9 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng hay b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y - Getafe. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCLB\u00a0thu\u1ed9c v\u00f9ng ngo\u1ea1i \u00f4 th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Madrid n\u00e0y b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn sau khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c x\u1ebfp v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 8 v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111ua tranh r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Europa League trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng cu\u1ed1i. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Getafe m\u00f9a n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p th\u00eam n\u1eefa. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Bordalas c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu\u00a0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 g\u1ed3m 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSo v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV\u00a0Lopetegui c\u00f3 hai s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ch\u1eb3ng r\u00f5 v\u00ec y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n hay \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Nacho Fernandez thay th\u1ebf Varane \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Dani Ceballos chi\u1ebfm ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Casemiro \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric v\u1eabn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN chi\u1ebfm l\u0129nh th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5 ph\u00e1t s\u00fang \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Gareth Bale v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1 b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Isco v\u00e0o ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4, b\u00ecnh t\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i nh\u1eb1m v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c cao song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Soria \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tung ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale Asensio\" title=\"Bale Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4F385B4000000578-6076597-image-a-7_1534714784345.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bale \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 sau pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Asensio</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 c\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed5i l\u00ean b\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh Getafe. Ph\u00fat 16, Marcelo t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Bale lao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Soria nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e0 ngang. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 20 th\u00ec Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Thay v\u00ec c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, Bale \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u1ea9u v\u1ecb b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch d\u1ea1t sang tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o trong h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Benzema nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Soria \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng ra. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Dani Carvajal v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong tay, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Real c\u00e0ng t\u1ecf ra l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch Getafe. B\u00f3ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 l\u0103n b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n Getafe. Ph\u00fat 33, trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, Sergio Ramos \"bay gi\u1eefa ng\u00e2n h\u00e0\" v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng sau pha tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Getafe. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 mau ch\u00f3ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng Ramos \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch (nh\u00ecn c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady) m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c ra l\u00e0 Benzema (ng\u01b0\u1eddi chuy\u1ec1n cho\u00a0Ramos) \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft hi\u1ec7p 1 th\u00ec v\u1ed1n trong tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN\u00a0v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n \u00edt \u1ecfi d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9. Ph\u1ea3i h\u01a1n 5 ph\u00fat sau khi hi\u1ec7p 2 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, Real Madrid m\u1edbi gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh, sao tr\u1ebb Marco Asensio - c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a Real Madrid - c\u0103ng ngang v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m cho Gareth Bale d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Getafe.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui co man khoi dau suon se voi Real Madrid o La Liga 2018/19\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf La Liga 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4F385BC300000578-6076597-image-a-9_1534715056208.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Lopetegui c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi Real Madrid \u1edf La Liga 2018/19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee9u nguy cho\u00a0Getafe sau pha ra ch\u00e2n c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Asensio. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Real v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng so v\u1edbi Getafe, Los Blancos v\u1eabn \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c. Bale v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t thong dong sau khi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o b\u1eadt l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, ph\u00fat 75, n\u1ebfu Alejo ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nhanh h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t nh\u1ecbp th\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Real v\u1edbi pha lao v\u00e0o d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh sau qu\u1ea3 c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, d\u00e0n sao Real th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111i b\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u00e0 Getafe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 song r\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec bi\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2-0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec cho \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c. V\u1eady l\u00e0, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra khi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u00fd t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn b\u1edfi Getafe h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn thua xa v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 \"g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3\" l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nReal Madrid (4-3-3): </strong>Keylor Navas; Dani Carvajal, Nacho, Sergio Ramos, Marcelo; Dani Ceballos (Luka Modric 71'), Toni Kroos, Isco (Casemiro 58'); Gareth Bale, Karim Benzema, Marco Asensio.<br>\r\n<strong>Getafe (4-5-1):</strong> David Soria; Damian Suarez, Bruno Gonzalez, Djene Dakonam, Leandro Cabrera; Francisco Portillo (Iv\u00e1n Alejo 64'), Mauro Arambarri, Gaku Shibasaki, Nemanja Maksimovic, Amath Ndiaye (Jaime Mata 58'); Jorge Molina (Angel 72').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5669","checkdouble":"194842"},{"date":"06:15 20/08","title":"Guardiola \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Mourinho: \"Man City kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ec9a mai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Manchester City m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ghi l\u1ea1i h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Man Utd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi tr\u00edch \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn derby Manchester l\u00e0 \u201ct\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1ef1ng xe bus\u201d.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/guardiola-dong-y-mourinho-man-city-khong-the-mua-dang-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean HLV Jose Mourinho b\u00ean kia th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf c\u00f4ng khai: \u201cAnh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m phim hay m\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, trong khi t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong b\u1ed9 phim \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Pep Guardiola, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gay g\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch m\u1ec9a mai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Man City 6-1 Huddersfield:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Jose r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd. \u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee7 \u00fd c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi l\u1ea1i trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m phim \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ec9a x\u00f3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jose m\u00e0.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">M\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Huddersfield t\u1ea1m \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Premier League 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Liverpool ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00eam nay. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-khinh-bi-man-city-va-doi-tien-catxe-dong-phim-172-194838.html\">Mourinho khinh b\u1ec9 Man City v\u00e0... \u0111\u00f2i ti\u1ec1n c\u00e1t-x\u00ea \u0111\u00f3ng phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua nh\u1ee5c: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5668","checkdouble":"194850"},{"date":"03:59 20/08","title":"Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"ctl00_m_contentBody_sp_title\" class=\"sp_title\" style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">Pogba l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a M.U</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n</span><br style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19, CLB Man United \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu Brighton &amp; Hove Albion.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Glenn Murray, Shane Duffy v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pascal Gross&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Brighton gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Man Utd. Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba\" title=\"Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/pogba-len-tieng-xin-loi-sau-tran-thua-bac-nhuoc-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1i t\u00f4i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00ean tr\u00ean. Th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn M.U li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i&rdquo;, Pogba n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn M.U x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng sai s\u00f3t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton. &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ed7i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay, v\u00e0 Brighton \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 khi thi\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, M.U x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 10 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3, Pogba v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Tottenham Hotspur v\u00e0o 02h00 ng\u00e0y 28/08 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Highlight: Brighton 2-0 MU (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279543\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/20/brighton-manutd.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;mute=false&amp;vtype=1&amp;playType=0&amp;_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&amp;_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&amp;postroll=true&amp;replay=true&amp;nonVol=true&amp;volume=0.6&amp;boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&amp;nopre=true&amp;midroll=0.8;20s&amp;urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-brighton-3-2-man-utd-pogba-ghi-ban-tren-cham-phat-den-20180819142040755.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong-172-194846.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-martial-chi-duoc-thi-dau-vi-sanchez-chan-thuong-172-194846.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Martial ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn Brighton.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cap-trung-ve-mu-bi-bo-doi-huyen-thoai-tong-si-va-sau-tham-bai-o-brighton-172-194848.html\">C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 MU b\u1ecb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng s\u1ec9 v\u1ea3 sau th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i \u1edf Brighton</span><br>\r\nEric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a Gary Neville v\u00e0 Paul Scholes sau tr\u1eadn thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5667","checkdouble":"194851"}]}